优化粒子标签的显示逻辑。例如，使用碰撞检测算法避免标签重叠，或在粒子数量较少时调整标签位置。示例代码：
```javascript
function drawSim() {
  // ...现有代码...
  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
    // ...现有代码...
    ctx.fillStyle = '#e0f2fe';
    ctx.font = '13px sans-serif';
    const label = i < n * r / 100 ? '新' : '原';
    const labelX = x - 8;
    const labelY = y + 5;
    // 检查标签是否重叠
    let overlap = false;
    for (let j = 0; j < i; j++) {
      const dx = labelX - labels[j].x;
      const dy = labelY - labels[j].y;
      if (Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy) < 10) {
        overlap = true;
        break;
      }
    }
    if (!overlap) {
      ctx.fillText(label, labelX, labelY);
      labels.push({x: labelX, y: labelY});
    }
  }
  // ...现有代码...
}
```

