完成 'spinWheel' 函数的代码，确保转盘能够正常旋转。例如，添加旋转动画逻辑：
```javascript
function spinWheel(){
  if(spinning) return;
  spinning = true;
  const totalRot = Math.PI * 2 * 5 + Math.random() * Math.PI * 2;
  let currentRot = 0;
  const spinSpeed = totalRot / 100;
  const spinInterval = setInterval(() => {
    currentRot += spinSpeed;
    drawSpinner(currentRot);
    if(currentRot >= totalRot){
      clearInterval(spinInterval);
      spinning = false;
      // 添加转盘停止后的逻辑
    }
  }, 10);
}
```

